# SPA fallback for dynamic deck routes (/decks/<id>).
# Static files (e.g. /home.html, /decks.html, /decks/new.html, /sw.js) are
# served as-is because Cloudflare Pages checks for existing files before
# evaluating redirect rules. Only paths under /decks/ that have no matching
# file fall through to index.html, where Expo Router's client-side routing
# reads location.pathname and renders /decks/[id].
/decks/*    /index.html   200
